# Implementation Report for draft-ietf-idr-bgpls-inter-as-topology-ext 

### **Vendor or Open Source Implementations**
H3C and the network controller R&D team from China Telecom have implemented all the protocol extensions that described in the draft as the followings:

Stub Link NLRI
Remote AS Number TLV
IPv4 Remote ASBR ID
IPv6 Remote ASBR ID

All the codepoints use the number assigned by the IANA.

We have also orgainized the interoperability test between the device and the controller, and the controller can parse correclty the information that is reported by the underly device from H3C, based on the description in the draft.
